quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  42,1,"Haa, miim."
  42,2,"Ain, siin, qaaf."
  42,3,"Ko wano nii woni ko Allah Te…ó…óu…óo, √Ďee√Īo oon wahayiniri e maa, e …ďeen adinoo…ďe maa."
  42,4,"Ko KaŇčko woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuji e ka leydi. Ko KaŇčko kadi woni Toowu…óo, maw…óo oon."
  42,5,"Kammuuji …óiin no e…ď…ďa seekorgol dow majji, hara Malaa'ika'en no subbunhinanora yettugol Joomi ma…ď…ďe, …ďe imsinanoo won…ďe ka leydi …ďeen. Ngandee pellet, ko Allah woni kaforoowo, jurmotoo…óo otoo…óo On."
  42,6,"∆Āeen non jogitii…ďe yi…ó…ďe goo ga Makko, Allah ko deenu…óo …ďe. A wonaani deenoowo …ďe."
  42,7,"Ko wano noon Min wahayniri e maa…óa, janngeteende e aarabu, fii yo a jeertin yim…ďe neene ca'e …óen e won…ďe takko mayre …ďeen, jerrtinaa fii √Īalnde dental nden, - nde sikke alaa e mu'um - Fedde goo ka Aljnna, fedde goo kadi ka Yiite."
  42,8,"Si Allah haajuno, O wa…óayno …ďe mofte goote. Kono himo oon mo O muuyi ka Yurmeende makko. Too√Īoo…ďe …ďeen non, gi…óo alanaa …ďe, wonaa ballo."
  42,9,"Kaa …ďe njogiti yi…ó…ďe goo ga makko? Awa ko Allah woni Gi…óo on, ko KaŇčko wuurnitata maay…ďe …ďeen; ko KaŇčko kadi woni ka…ótan…óo kala hu'unde."
  42,10,"Kala ko luutondir…óon e fii mun, haray √Īaawoore mum nden ko ka Allah woni. Ko on moo…óon Allah, woni Joomi am; ko e makko mi fawii, ko ka makko kadi mi ruttorta [tuubugol]."